sentence.text: When stratified by tumor histology, three SNPs (ENO1 rs2274971A > G, PFKM rs11168417C > T, and cellular response to reactive oxygen species rs3785921G > A) were significantly associated with OS and/or DFS only in squamous cell carcinoma, whereas canonical glycolysis rs1132173C > T exhibited a significant association with survival outcomes only in adenocarcinoma.
